ted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973850/extras/0ad5b91dc29321006ab2b50e554d1d31.poster.avif?t=1726304066\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973850/extras/0ad5b91dc29321006ab2b50e554d1d31.webm?t=1726304066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1973850/extras/0ad5b91dc29321006ab2b50e554d1d31.mp4?t=1726304066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Every levels can completable but this needs very good reflexes and most important a so strong patience!</strong><br><strong>Are you still thinking you can pass this Challenge? Buy now and enjoy your suffer!</strong>",
